Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.85,0:02:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,O alvo é uma Gauna tipo colmeia, com cerca de 830 metros de comprimento.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela abriga 27 Gaunas individuais dentro de si.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.74,0:02:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A presença de uma Gauna Mestra é certa.{not just likely, there has to be one}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.61,0:02:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Destruí-la é seu objetivo principal.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Seu objetivo secundário é cortar o rabo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fazer isso reduziria significativamente o tamanho da placenta delas.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.00,0:02:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O inimigo desta vez pode ser grande, mas temos experiência lutando contra as Gaunas.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Não tema.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.67,0:02:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,1.000 quilômetros até que o esquadrão de subjugação alcance o alvo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, acionem seus propulsores de retrocesso.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.84,0:02:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.68,0:02:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos executar sua estratégia agora.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.85,0:02:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Desativando propulsores de retrocesso em 15 segundos.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparem-se para dissolver a formação.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.73,0:02:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,O esquadrão de Kunato tentará imediatamente\Ncortar o rabo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,O esquadrão de Imada os apoiará.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.99,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos os outros, procurem o Gauna Mestre na testa da criatura.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.16,0:03:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Desmanchar a formação!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos, sigam-me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.01,0:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidades, espalhem-se e fiquem atentos aos braços placentários.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Agarrem na base do rabo!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.85,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.99,0:03:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Coma isso!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Núcleo exposto!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que não vamos progredir\Naté matar o Gauna Mestre.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.92,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Samari!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Atrás de você!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.80,0:04:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,115, 013, dano severo!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,O esquadrão de Kunato está fazendo\Nprogresso na cauda?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.73,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles chegaram e agora estão preparando os explosivos.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunato, apresse-se e corte isso!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunato falando. Três cargas estão prontas.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Relatem o progresso!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.62,0:04:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshijiro, três cargas!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Honoka, duas cargas!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze, quatro cargas!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,O esquadrão de Kunato colocou 12 cargas.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom. Recuem imediatamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Detonem as cargas!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.92,0:04:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.75,0:04:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidades, recuem.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Detonem suas cargas no meu sinal.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Não percam!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado!
