Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos fazer isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparem-se para a detonação.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Detonar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Detonando!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Detonação confirmada.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As cargas de 08 a 12 se soltaram.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Detonação simultânea falhou.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.57,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze {**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A gente não ia fazer isso junto?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo, Tanikaze?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunato ainda não deu o sinal!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,É Kunato falando.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Falhamos em cortar a cauda.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.33,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Abortando missão.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Aguardando ordens adicionais.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A atenção dos Gaunas está na cauda dele!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Esquadrões Kunato e Imada, recuem imediatamente!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.76,0:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,O Gauna está reagindo à detonação.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.09,0:05:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As cargas de 01 a 07 se soltaram.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Esquadrão Imada, esquadrão Kunato, limpem a área imediatamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrem em formação de 118 quadros!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,O Gauna está detonando as cargas perdidas!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.31,0:05:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,052 e 219 ficaram presos nas explosões.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandone a cauda.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidades, retirada temporária.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Reagrupar-se à distância.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidades, recuar.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.95,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nós nos reagruparemos e retomaremos nosso ataque.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze, o que você está fazendo?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos recuando!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está me ouvindo, Tanikaze?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.96,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Espera...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Eu não...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze{**-kun}, espere!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Não, Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Deixa ele!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0!]
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...se o rabo tivesse sido seccionado.{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}{line needs changing for batch}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não concordo.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.98,0:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Não foi só culpa de Tanikaze\Nque o rabo não tenha sido seccionado.{line needs changing for batch}
