Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze, o que você está fazendo?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos recuando!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está me ouvindo, Tanikaze?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Espera...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Eu não...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze{**-kun}, espere!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Não, Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.05,0:07:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Larguem ele!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0!]
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.18,0:07:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Acorda! Por favor!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.39,0:07:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está me ouvindo?\NIsso é uma ordem direta!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0!]
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.98,0:07:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Só um pouco mais.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Não, Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Volta!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0!]
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Corram!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Não...
