Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Como ele está?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.23,0:10:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Um...]
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.64,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele não viria?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.77,0:10:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Alguém precisa colocar algum senso nele.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.78,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou tentar amanhã.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.65,0:10:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso não é o que Hoshijiro teria querido.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Hiyama[T2]...]
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.08,0:10:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gaunas nos deixarão sozinhos se desarmarmos!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.04,0:10:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gaunas nos deixarão sozinhos se desarmarmos!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.33,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sidônia deve desarmar completamente!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sidônia deve desarmar completamente!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.97,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Embora as pesadas perdas da última batalha tenham enfraquecido os protestos anti-militares,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:08.39,Sign - Corbel,,0,0,0,,{\fnAmble\blur0.6\fs30\b1\pos(687.111,530.333)}Manifestações Antimilitares Cada Vez Mais Violentas{look at last ep for similar sign}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.31,0:11:08.39,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an4\blur0.5\c&H797979&\fnZekton\b1\fs30\pos(265.778,565.11)}Sidonia\NNotícias Públicas[T1]
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.76,0:11:07.89,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,a liderança militar anunciou uma significativa mudança de pessoal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:15.61,Sign - Corbel,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs30\frz0.2787\b0\pos(313.6,88.4)\c&HFFFFFF&}{TS 11:08 all rows}Novos Pilotos
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:15.61,Sign - Corbel,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs30\frz0.2787\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(643.782,89.855)}{TS 11:08 all rows}Novos Pilotos
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:15.61,Sign - Corbel,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs30\frz0.2787\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(970.327,88.4)}{TS 11:08 all rows}Novos Pilotos
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.52,0:11:15.27,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Complementando os sobreviventes da batalha anterior estão estes quinze ex-estagiários.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.27,0:11:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Além disso, o ex-oficial executivo,\NSeii Ichirou, está se juntando aos esquadrões de pilotos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:21.11,Sign - Corbel,,0,0,0,,{\fry358\blur0.5\pos(846.222,227.556)\b1}Nova Designação
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:21.11,Sign - Corbel,,0,0,0,,[T0Seii\NIchirou]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:21.11,Sign - Corbel,,0,0,0,,{\fry358\blur0.5\b1\pos(845.266,405.778)}Novo Cargo: Esquadrões de Pilotos do Sul
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:21.11,Sign - Corbel,,0,0,0,,{\fry358\blur0.5\b1\pos(851.666,492.178)}Cargo Anterior: Oficial Executivo do QG de Sidonia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:21.11,Sign - Corbel,,0,0,0,,{\fry358\blur0.5\b1\c&H6C6C6C&\pos(389.777,511.845)}Esquadrões de Pilotos do Sul
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:21.11,Sign - Corbel,,0,0,0,,{\fry358\blur0.5\b1\c&H6C6C6C&\pos(389.777,551.591)}Número de Identificação Sei-026
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx80}...{\r}O novo executivo saiu—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:28.04,Sign - MinchoB,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\blur0.6\pos(639.314,368.286)\c&H424B4B&}{TS 11:26}T{*\c&H4F5958&}a{*\c&H5C6766&}n{*\c&H697574&}i{\c&H768482&}k{*\c&H64716F&}a{*\c&H535E5D&}z{\c&H424B4B&}e Nagate
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Abre essa maldita porta!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Você consegue me ouvir, Nagate?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou entrando!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Este quarto está uma bagunça!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,E o que é toda essa poeira?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou limpar isso agora.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.64,0:11:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Endireita-te.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é um piloto agora.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Um piloto...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.08,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate... Você quer ser um piloto para proteger Sidônia, não é?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.83,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Então você precisa da determinação para isso, mesmo que seja difícil.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.71,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gauna não vão esperar suas lágrimas secarem.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.13,0:12:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.39,0:12:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.52,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou resolver essa bagunça.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Recomendo que você se afaste um pouco.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Mas a porta...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Deixa que eu cuido disso.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.40,0:12:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Anda, vá.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou deixá-lo com você agora.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.65,0:12:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.15,0:12:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá, Nagate!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.33,0:12:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Então, o que os manifestantes estão planejando?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.42,0:12:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uma grande manifestação está sendo planejada, e cada vez mais desejam deixar Sidônia.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,À medida que os encontros com os Gauna se tornam mais frequentes,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,a crença de que eles só nos atacam por causa dos Kabizashis que empunhamos se espalhará.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.05,0:13:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gauna não virão se nós {\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}jogarmos fora os Kabizashis", hein...?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.10,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Do ponto de vista deles, essa é a única maneira que podemos realizar nossa viagem planejada até o sistema estelar Lem.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Absurdo.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.99,0:13:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos que desejam deixar\NSidônia podem fazê-lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas eu não pararei a guerra.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.70,0:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Enquanto os Gaunas existirem,\Nnós não podemos reconstruir nossa pátria.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.62,0:13:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu emitirei as ordens pertinentes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chame Yure.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.67,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Farei.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Você me chamou?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.88,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Doutor Yure, realizaremos a cerimônia de partida em\Na em breve.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Iniciem os preparativos imediatamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Farei.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Você deve estar com fome, Nagate.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fique aqui!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.12,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sete mortos em combate.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu soube.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.58,DefaultAlt,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}{nagate thoughts}{\i1}Este é o lugar onde...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamar isso de grande vitória é uma piada.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.92,0:14:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,E não há planos para\Nrecuperar os feridos, certo?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.84,0:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Eu acho que isso é...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqui está.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.18,0:14:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Para uma garota fofa como você,\Nas bebidas são por nossa conta.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.39,0:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas eu não sou uma garota.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.31,0:14:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não consigo parar de comer!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Hoshijiro...]
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Criminoso de guerra!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.87,0:15:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Você sabe quantos pilotos morreram por sua causa?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não tem vergonha de si mesmo?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nunca mais pilote!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está bem, Nagate?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, não!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está sangrando!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estou bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu dou conta disso.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos para outro lugar.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.73,0:15:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Um gigante gasoso errante...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.07,0:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Origem da Gauna tipo colmeia G488.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.78,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}A Gauna que escapou retornou ali...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa Yuhata, na ponte de comando.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.55,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Coloque o planeta errante N 68203L na tela.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado, XO Midorikawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.85,0:16:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Distância relativa até N 68203L\Nis de 700.000 quilômetros.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Relatório.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.94,0:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Este é o planeta para onde os Gaunas fugiram após a última batalha.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.15,0:16:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Numerosos Gaunas podem se esconder em seu gás.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lançar um ataque preventivo enquanto ainda estivermos à distância.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Destruam o planeta.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso fará com que os Gaunas saiam.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Use o míssil antiplaneta.{I want an exterminatus.}{use the anti planetary guided projectile}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,O míssil antiplaneta?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Objeções?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Não...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare um míssil antiplaneta.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.84,0:16:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.84,0:16:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparando o míssil antiplaneta.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.80,0:16:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Míssil carregado com uma ogiva de implosão de alta pressão.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Movendo para o tubo de lançamento.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Abrindo o anteparo frontal sete.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Aberto.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo o pessoal, preparem-se para o lançamento.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.90,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Repito.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo o pessoal, preparem-se para o lançamento.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.61,0:16:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Prontos para o lançamento.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.36,0:16:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Planeta errante N 68203L alvo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.03,0:16:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos prontos.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fogo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lançando míssil!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.26,0:17:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A trajetória do míssil está dentro da margem de erro.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.59,0:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue observando o míssil até o impacto.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.52,0:17:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.06,0:17:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Não é isso que eu desejo!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é talentoso.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mais talentoso do que qualquer um antes de você.\N
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não quero!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordem da capitã.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.03,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu quero ser um piloto no lugar do meu irmão!\N
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.71,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Midorikawa...]
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Se você deseja lutar contra os Gauna,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.26,0:17:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,então você não serve como piloto.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.18,0:18:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Distância até o planeta: 3.000 quilômetros.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Monitorando o míssil até o impacto.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.36,0:18:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Impacto em 5 segundos.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}3...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.74,0:18:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}2...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}1...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.11,0:18:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Impacto.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.03,0:18:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Penetrando o alvo.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Atravessando camadas de gás.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.58,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}O poder de aniquilar um planeta...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.29,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,E ainda assim, o núcleo de uma Gauna permanecerá intacto.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Contato com o núcleo do planeta.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Implosão confirmada.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Destruição confirmada.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.93,0:18:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Repassando.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.05,0:18:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Escaneie a área em busca de anormalidades.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.93,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A-1-5 e B-4-3, nada.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,C-2-9, nada.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.56,0:18:51.27,DefaultAlt,,0,0,0,,K-3-7, nada.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,S-4-1, nada.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.11,0:18:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Anormalidade!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dois corpos, com tamanho menor que um quilômetro.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.57,0:18:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Não, três!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,O gás está muito denso.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu quero uma análise de imagem!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.62,0:19:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Reúna um esquadrão de subjugação e mande-os sair em missão.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Deixo a composição para você.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tem um gosto muito bom.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está comendo de novo, finalmente.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.89,0:19:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Esse ferimento na sua cabeça realmente está bem?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, agora está tudo bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.90,0:19:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos voltar agora.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Não queremos preocupar Hiyama{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.20,0:19:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fico feliz por ter conseguido te animar um pouco.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.62,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Izana.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.29,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnHallandale Stencil JL\b1\fs46\blur4\3a&H44&\c&H559DA4&\3c&H0B7279&\frx6\fscx61\fscy63\frz13.88\pos(662.999,249.666)}Expedição
