Dialogue: 3,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.29,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnHallandale Stencil JL\b1\fs46\blur0.6\c&H75ECEE&\frx6\fscx61\fscy63\frz13.88\pos(662.999,249.666)}Expedição
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Expedição?{ts}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que sempre tem que ser você?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu ainda consigo pilotar.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu voltarei, Izana.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,O esquadrão de Nakazono,\Nembarquem em suas unidades.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.49,0:20:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Plataforma de Lançamento Sul Dois,\No esquadrão de Samari, embarquem em suas unidades.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.50,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,O esquadrão de Kunato,\NTanikaze Nagate foi atrasado.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0...]
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nossa...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Foi reparado...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.85,0:20:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lançar o esquadrão de Nakazono e\No esquadrão de Samari assim que estiverem prontos.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,É Tanikaze Nagate falando.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.68,0:20:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu entrei na minha estrutura.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunato falando.\NMeu esquadrão está pronto para o lançamento.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lento demais.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.65,0:20:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lancem-nos imediatamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.98,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as estruturas, lancem e partam!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.49,0:21:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuhata?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.74,0:21:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrem na formação\Nimmediately after launch.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.54,0:21:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tente recuperar algum tempo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.69,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.70,0:21:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Não pense nem em tentar me culpar.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu só luto contra os Gaunas.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nada mais.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
